name: Brainta: It Is Not Real
description:
You deceased due to an unfortunate accident and wake up in a virtual world. Instructions were given, but are they telling the truth?

When you are playing in browser, please full screen :D

Controls :

WASD - Move

Mouse - Look around

E - Interact

All keys, sensibility, graphic quality, and volume can be modify in setting menu.

This game is made in 7 days for Brackey's Game Jam

I am a coder and I am soloing so the story isn't long. (12 - 15 mins)

Credits:

3D models - Everything is from Unity Asset Store

Music- from QQMusic

Sound effects - from https://ibaotu.com/

Code - I wrote all the codes and thanks to infinite tutorials on YouTube

Hope you guys have fun, and if not, sorry for the unpleasant.

:)
